A HONÜ WORLD

HONÜ (Hawaiian word for sea turtle) embodies a life motto: “Slow & Steady Wins The Race.”

His versatility shines through in seamless transitions between house and bass music, creating a unique sonic landscape. He’s landed releases on labels backed by EDM giants such as Steve Aoki, Don Diablo, Wax Motif, Kyle Watson, Boogie T, Dr. Fresch, and more.

Each set fuses pulsating house rhythms and deep basslines, delivering unforgettable experiences. Whether headlining festivals or spinning in intimate clubs, the energy and passion he brings lights up every stage.

The slogan “Break out of your shell, it’ll set you free” defines his approach to life, one that embraces living fully in the moment.

The Turtle Club stands as a community built for dreamers, reminding fans they’re not alone in life’s ocean and encouraging them to “Never stop chasing your dream, even if you’re as slow as a turtle.”

